# Frontend stage-specific overrides — copy & rename to `.env.local` /
# `.env.dev` / `.env.int` / `.env.prod` and edit. Selected at BUILD/RUN
# time via `APP_ENV`, injected by `scripts/with-env.mjs`.
#
# IMPORTANT: NEXT_PUBLIC_* values are baked into the client bundle at
# build time. Each stage needs its own `next build` run — that's what
# `npm run build:dev | build:int | build:prod` do for you.
#
# Loading order (FIRST wins):
#   1. process.env (CI overrides)             ← already-set wins
#   2. apps/web/.env.${APP_ENV}              ← injected by with-env.mjs
#   3. apps/web/.env.local                    ← Next.js convention
#   4. apps/web/.env.production / .env.development  ← Next mode files
#   5. apps/web/.env                          ← Next base file
#
# Common overrides:
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.smart-apply.io/api/v1
# NEXT_PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=0x...
